<section class="slide" id="slide-1">
  <div class="section-tag">01 · Earning the Meeting</div>
  <div class="section-title">How I Booked Leon Faulstroh</div>
  <div class="section-subtitle">The exact strategy I used — from research to the call.</div>

  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
